attr.attrdef: - Primary Street Name - The legal street name as assigned by local address authority. - STREETNAME does not include the street type of a named street. - STREETNAME does not include the suffix direction of a coordinate street. Suffix direction belongs in SUFFIX. - STREETNAME might incorporate a Street Name Pre Modifier and/or a Street Name Post Modifier (which do not have their own separate fields). In some cases, Street Name Pre Modifier might be acceptable in PREFIX field. - STREETNAME does not include street aliases.
